{"type": "article", "id": 31153, "title": "American Apparel 要卖，以及，藤原浩与星巴克做了个联名杯 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-18T02:21:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4029, "name": "American Eagle"}, {"id": 31647, "name": "DPM"}, {"id": 31648, "name": "Thymes"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 3154, "name": "Levi’s"}, {"id": 3801, "name": "I.T"}, {"id": 9086, "name": "Starbucks"}, {"id": 21504, "name": "Univision"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160818094142ATsYMZKhbODCnIGN.jpg", "contents": "<h6>一些重要的新闻：</h6><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/thymes-dpm-fragrance-merger-formed-curio-castanea-partners-bath-body-beauty-10508042/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>香水品牌 Thymes 和 DPM 宣布合并</b></a> | 合并后的公司为 Curio，这将是一个全新的售卖身体、家居香氛的平台。Curio 将保留 Thymes 这个品牌，以及 DPM 旗下的 Aspen Bay and Capri Blue 两个香氛品牌。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/financial/american-eagle-q2-beat-wall-street-estimates-10507907/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>休闲服装品牌 American Eagle 第二季度收入大涨</b></a> | 截止至 7 月 30 日，American Eagle 第二季度净收入增长了 25%，至 4160 万美元，大大高于华尔街预期。该公司称，更低的成本和更高的定价，是 American Eagle 实现增长的主要原因。&nbsp;</p><p></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/univision-buys-gawker-media-for-135-million-10507953/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Univision 传媒集团收购 Gawker Media </b></a>| Univision 斥资 1350 万美元，买下了 Gawker Media。Univision 是美国最大的西班牙语电视网，Gawker Media 则是由 Nick Denton 创办的全球知名的新闻传媒博客，也是全球最有价值的商业博客之一。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/american-apparel-sale-banker-houlihan-lokey-10508584/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>American Apparel 欲出售</b></a> | 去年十月，American Apparel 在经历了销量下滑、债务负担沉重之后申请破产保护。近日，American Apparel 聘请了精品投行 Houlihan Lokey ，为它寻找买家。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/sales-l-brands-second-quarter-earnings-10508477/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>维多利亚的秘密的母公司 L Brands 集团第二季度销量大涨</b></a> |  由于电商卖得不错，L Brands 第二季度销量上涨了 24.7%，净收入为 25.2 亿美元，去年同期则为 20.2 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Tommy Hilfiger  发布与超模 Gigi Hadid 合作设计的第一个概念系列 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/lookbook/gigi-hadid-tommy-hilfiger-collaboration-first-look-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TOMMYxGIGI</a> 的宣传照。该系列延续了 Tommy 的街头美式风格，Gigi 为其新加入了一些个人的时尚元素。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100612vw2Mi5bAhtzjf4dg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100604kwPsYTdLCOgDZF6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100554pbEdtN1HVuGocMXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100547vOl4MRbLQ0oGYImu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100539yi7qO6LzI4Fvdhto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/fragment-design-x-starbucks-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本潮流教父藤原浩与 Starbucks 联名推出玻璃杯</a>。此款玻璃杯在设计上采用了耐热玻璃，结合了不锈钢底托和把手，并印有招牌的闪电 logo。将于 8 月 18 日起，在日本的 9 家星巴克门店及官网发售，每套两只，售价 4500 日元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100529mha4XP8OEYvGeIDu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100522pZdOaHxNTbWvVRXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100515vGuwgOEXqhZMIodK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Levi’s 推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/levis-505c-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 505™ C 全新款式</a>，灵感来自 ROLLING STONES、THE RAMOSE 等摇滚巨星，打造不羁的牛仔风格。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100455vGiZWklBpNQy6M8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608181004487zV45dWoaNwA93nh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081810044131qmjPcTRuWDIzaV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100435Mwm6RanpGosUXxqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100429tMXwkfCnZEBWcGOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>I.T 发布了 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/i-t-2016-fw-preview\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬 lookbook</a>&nbsp;。以军事风格为主题，包括了OAMC、WHIZ、ALMOST BLACK、FACETASM、N.HOOLYWOOD 等人气品牌。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100408rWqgcdDRNt4nETK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100402C1UGKL6VXmqseJ0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608181003543ou4bsSGRUzK9E8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100347ECN0i4vfKyL39XDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100341Obyu85QIHXdD1RWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Visvim 旗下鞋类系列 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/visvim-skagway-hi-fw16\" rel=\"nofollow\">SKAGWAY HI 发布了 2016 秋冬季新鞋款</a>。主打复古风，采用了丹宁材质和撞色设计。定价为 570 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608181003083kzmQJglAcyLb5OM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\" aria-dropeffect=\"move\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"option\" aria-grabbed=\"false\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818100301JWXbkBPqVKQIpfL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}